result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleOk()"
  @cancel="handleCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="名称"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'name',
          {
            rules:[
              { required: true, message: '请输入名称' },
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.name : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="状态"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'status',
          {
            rules: [
            { required: true, message: '请输入名称' },
               { max:128,message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.status : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="代理合同时间"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'contract_time',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.contract_time : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="预计时间"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
        'estimated_time',
        {
          rules: [
            { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
          ],
          validateTrigger: 'blur',
          initialValue: record ? record.estimated_time : null
        }
      ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="公告时间"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'announce_time',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个字符以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.announce_time : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="招标控制价"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'control_price',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.control_price : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="招标时间"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'bid_time',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.bid_time : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="中标单位"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'bid_company',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:64, message: '长度在64个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.bid_company : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="联系人"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'linkman',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.linkman : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="电话"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'phone',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.phone : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="进场时间"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'approach_time',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.approach_time : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="代理费"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'agency_fee',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:16, message: '长度在16个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.agency_fee : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="中标金额"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'bid_price',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:256, message: '长度在256个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.bid_price : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>

  </a-form>
</a-modal>
